Classification: Scripted
Genre: Comedy | Sketch/Improv
Status: New Series
Network: BBC TWO ( United Kingdom)
Airs: Tuesdays at 10:00 pm
Runtime: 30 Minutes
Premiere: September 28, 2010

Harry And Paul is a comedy sketch series featuring the talents of Harry Enfield and Paul Whitehouse. The series features a variety of new characters, and one or two old favourites in different short sketches.
